      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Dissolve half the&nbsp;<span class=\"text-danger\">[whole]</span>&nbsp;<strong>stock cube</strong> with 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span>&nbsp;boiled water in a heatproof bowl&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>couscous</strong> to the stock, cover and set aside&nbsp;</p>",
