            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chicken</strong> to a bowl with the<strong>&nbsp;spring onion</strong>,<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and the remaining<strong> stock cube</strong></p>\r\n<p>Mix very well and set aside</p>",
