    {
      "instruction": "<p>Roll the<strong> lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice!) and cut in half</p>\r\n<p>Combine the juice of half a&nbsp;<span class=\"text-danger\">[whole]</span> <strong>lime</strong> with the<strong> saffron</strong> and <strong>honey</strong> - this is your glaze</p>",
