    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat with 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chicken</strong> mixture and cook for 5-7 min or until cooked through</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
