    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>\r\n<p>Fluff the couscous, add the chopped <strong>coriander</strong>&nbsp;and the juice of the remaining&nbsp;<strong>lime</strong></p>\r\n<p>Season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and stir in a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p>",
